    "en": {
      "title": "Fuel from Cipetco from tomorrow",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Ministry of Electricity and Energy says that fuel will be released from Cipetco fuel stations from tomorrow. As mentioned earlier, fuel will be issued according to the last digit of the vehicle number plate.",
        "Accordingly, fuel will be issued to vehicles with numbers 3, 4, 5 on the vehicle number plate tomorrow. However, fuel will be issued at 1500 rupees for motorcycles, 2000 rupees for three-wheelers and 7000 rupees for other vehicles."
      ],
